snippet.title: Salaar Teaser | Prabhas, Prashanth Neel, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Hombale Films, Vijay Kiragandur
snippet.description:
THE MOST VIOLENT MEN... CALLED ONE MAN... THE MOST VIOLENT üî•
Presenting our next feature #SalaarCeaseFire to the world

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Sep 28th,2023.

SALAAR MOVIE CREDITS:
Producer : Vijay Kiragandur
Story - Screenplay - Direction : Prashanth Neel 
Salaar Star Cast - Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Hassan
DOP : Bhuvan Gowda
Production Designer : Shivakumar - T L Venkatachalapathi 
Music : Ravi Basrur
Stunts : Anbarivu 
Costume Designer : Thota Vijay Bhaskar 
Executive Producers : KV Rama Rao - Karthik 
Editor : Ujwal Kulkarni 
Dialogues : Sandeep Reddy Bandla - Hanuman Chaudhary - DR Suri 
VFX Supervisor : Raghav Tamma Reddy 
Lyricist : Krishna Kanth 
 
Direction Team:

GOWRA CHANDRABABL NAIDU - AKASH THARGAAR - LIKHITH RAGHUVEER S- RAM REDDY MARELLA - SUPREME KRANTHI SURYA - FARMAN ULLA

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQA3TWG8mHLCRO_vFhMoYiV

Meeru malli malli raarammaanna istha re entry

Moodocchaaka aadaaligaa hushaaraina aata

Malli putti bhumeedhiki raane raavu nijam thelusuko
Pakka dhigi nidharleche prathi roju pandaga chusuko
Unna kastha time lo na antho intho anubhavichi po

snippet.title: #Salaar Rebelling with 100M+ views | Prabhas | Prashanth Neel | Hombale Films | Vijay Kiragandur
snippet.description:
Rebelling Worldwide with 100M+ views. This is just the beginning, lots more to come your way. Brace yourselves for the Most Violent Man.

#SalaarTeaser100MViews
#SalaarCeaseFire ‚ñ∂ https://youtu.be/bUR_FKt7Iso

THE  MOST VIOLENT MEN... CALLED ONE MAN... THE MOST VIOLENT üî•
Presenting our next feature #SalaarCeaseFire to the world

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Sep 28th,2023.

SALAAR MOVIE CREDITS:
Producer : Vijay Kiragandur
Story - Screenplay - Direction : Prashanth Neel 
Salaar Star Cast - Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Hassan

snippet.description:
Shiju Abdul Rasheed is an Indian actor who works in Malayalam and Telugu films. Shiju Abdul Rasheed is known by stage name Devi Shiju in Telugu films as Shiju Abdul Rasheed played a role in Kodi Ramakrishna's Devi. Shiju Abdul Rasheed has appeared in more than 50 films and several popular TV series. Shiju has a career that has spanned 14 years from Tollywood to Mollywood and on to an international movie. Shiju Abdul Rasheed was born on 4 August 1974 in Kerala, India. In 1996 was his debut and first success in a Tamil movie named Mahaprabhu, directed by A. Venkitesh. His performance as a villain in this movie gave him a major break in his career.

snippet.title: Yaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai | B Praak | Nawazuddin Siddiqui | Shehnaaz Gill | Jaani | Arvindr Khaira
snippet.description:
Desi Melodies presents ‚ÄòYaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai‚Äô, the second single from B Praak‚Äôs debut album, ‚ÄúZohrajabeen‚Äù. Reuniting after their super hit 'Baarish Ki Jaaye', the all-star team of Nawazuddin Siddiqui, BPraak, Jaani, and Arvindr Khaira is back with yet another heart-wrenching song that explores the complexities of romance, and the pain of its absence. Experience a melancholic journey in the voice of BPraak paired with soul-stirring lyrics and composition by Jaani and a short film by Arvindr Khaira featuring Nawazuddin Siddiqui and Shehnaaz Gill that embodies a bittersweet tale that can't be chased anymore, painting a picture of respectful regret.¬†Indulge your feelings in the beauty of this musical masterpiece, as it leaves you reflecting upon the significance of love and the poignancy of letting go.¬†

Listen to ‚ÄòYaar Ka Sataya Hua Hai‚Äô on your favourite streaming platform - https://umgindia.lnk.to/YKSHH

snippet.title: THE NUN II | OFFICIAL TRAILER
snippet.description:
On September 8th, the greatest evil in the conjuring universe returns #TheNun2

New Line Cinema brings you the horror thriller ‚ÄúThe Nun II,‚Äù the next chapter in the story of ‚ÄúThe Nun,‚Äù the highest grossing entry in the juggernaut $2 billion ‚ÄúThe Conjuring‚Äù Universe.

1956 ‚Äì France. A priest is murdered. An evil is spreading. The sequel to the worldwide smash hit follows Sister Irene as she once again comes face-to-face with Valak, the demon nun.

Taissa Farmiga (‚ÄúThe Nun,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Gilded Age‚Äù) returns as Sister Irene, joined by Jonas Bloquet (‚ÄúTirailleurs,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Nun‚Äù), Storm Reid (‚ÄúThe Last of Us,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Anna Popplewell (‚ÄúFairytale,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Chronicles of Narnia‚Äù trilogy) and Bonnie Aarons (reprising her role from ‚ÄúThe Nun‚Äù), surrounded by an ensemble cast of international talent.

Michael Chaves (‚ÄúThe Conjuring: The Devil Made Me Do It‚Äù) directs, from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing (‚ÄúEli,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Autopsy of Jane Doe‚Äù) and Akela Cooper (‚ÄúM3GAN,‚Äù ‚ÄúMalignant‚Äù),with a story by Cooper, based on characters created by James Wan & Gary Dauberman.

The Safran Company‚Äôs Peter Safran and Atomic Monster‚Äôs James Wan produce, continuing their collaboration as filmmakers on all of the previous ‚ÄúConjuring‚Äù films. ‚ÄúThe Nun II‚Äù is executive produced by Richard Brener, Dave Neustadter, Victoria Palmeri, Gary Dauberman, Michael Clear, Judson Scott and Michael Polaire.

Jhoom Digitally Presented by Spot-Less Skin With Ponds

A journey of JHOOM into the world of love, relationships, heartbreak, and sacrifice that centers around the lives of two souls who find love in a world of chaos and uncertainty that changes their lives forever. Aryaan is a young and handsome boy who holds a caring and possessive nature towards his friends. Despite having a traumatic past, Aryaan tries to smile through the worries of life and never steps back from helping his friends.

However, Aryaan's life takes an unexpected turn when he meets Maryam, a compassionate and kind-hearted woman who becomes a ray of sunshine in his life. As their relationship begin to flourish, Aryaan feels a change in himself and embraces the love that he had been deprived for so long.

Despite the significant age gap between them, Aryaan and Maryam's love for each other knows no bounds, and they embark on an unconventional journey together. Their love defies societal norms and expectations, challenging the prejudices and biases of those around them.

As their relationship progresses, their love is put to the ultimate test. Will they be able to overcome their challenges and sacrifices to stay together? Will their love stand the test of time and societal pressure? Is age just a number when it comes to love?

snippet.title: Triumph Speed 400 and Scrambler 400x First Impressions üáÆüá≥ | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, Bajaj and Triumph are now ready with their first jointly developed bike of 400cc, the speed 400. With just Rs 2, 33,000 ex-showroom this looks amazing on paper and for first 10,000 customers there is a discount of Rs 10,000 each. Not just that, in a joint conference, Bajaj and Triumph said that the scrambler 400x will be launched soon and a cafe racer version will follow. snippet.description: We finally got the opportunity to ride the most affordable and smallest Triumph ever made, This has been co-developed by Bajaj and Triumph to take on Royal Enfield's 350cc bikes and newly launched Harley Davidson X400. Amar Saxena is a businessman, and the managing director of prestigious Khaitan Fans Ltd., India. Using his wits, Amar manages to convince the Court that he is of unsound mind, and thus escapes being imprisoned, and ends up in an asylum. snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Khalasi | Aditya Gadhvi x Achint
snippet.description:
#Khalasi tells the tale of the limitless sailor who is set out to explore through the shores of Gujarat. The song speaks of his tenuous, adventurous voyage, his delightful experiences and his enthusiasm with which he takes on life while he is sailing away!

Headlining iconic music composer Achint Thakkar whose musical landscape tends to be inspired by the 70‚Äôs and aims to draw a narrative through his musical notes.  

He was joined by famous playback singer from Gujarat, Aditya Gadhvi. Known for singing in several languages and producing numerous chart hits that were singles. 

In addition to them, the song also boasts of Dhruv Visvanath, India‚Äôs premier solo percussive acoustic guitarist who also happens to be a professional singer-songwriter, and producer.  
Join them on this musical voyage.

Follow us on Instagram: Http://www.instagram.com/CokeStudioBharat

--------------------------------------------------------
Chalu Pandey arrives at Gada House and inquires about Jetha's condition. Jetha informs the Inspector that his issue has been resolved and that he no longer requires his aid. Chalu Pandey is enraged at Jetha for failing to inform him of the situation. Jetha describes the entire scenario to the cop. Jetha blames Bhide, claiming that calling the cops was his idea. Chalu Pandey demands to see Sundar's amusing act of scaring Jetha after learning about it. So Sundar and his companions dress up and put on a scary show.

snippet.title: RED & WHITE DRAGON FRUIT MILKSHAKE | Easy Milkshake Recipe | Ice Cream Fruit Dessert Recipe
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we make a delicious dragon fruit milkshake recipe using Red & White Dragon Fruits. We make this milkshake recipe quick and easy, but the complex process is grinding all dragon fruit pulp in a traditional stone grinder.

We add some sugar and ice cream to make this milkshake original!

The taste is Delicious!

Episode 3816: Bin Bulaye Mehman
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jetha and his team head to the police station to liberate Sundar, they are confronted by three strange beings who try to intimidate them. These people are later revealed to be Sundar and his crew, who were only playing a joke on them. Jetha inquires about Daya's return, and Sundar responds that he is unsure about her return to Gokuldham. Jetha is enraged with Sundar because he misses his wife. Champaklal calls Jetha to inquire about Sundar's whereabouts and is relieved to learn that he is safe. Sundar and his pals arrive at Gada's house and prepare to sleep, but who will sleep in the corridor? Watch the episode to see more of the amusing scenes!

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. Introducing Noufal and Umma, two individuals who have become beloved figures among Malayalis. The situation of even wanting to kill their own children has occurred in Umma's life. Their lives have been marked by incredible struggles, making their story one that resonates deeply with all who hear it.

‡¥á‡¥™‡µç‡¥™‡µã‡µæ ‡¥®‡¥ø‡¥ô‡µç‡¥ô‡µæ‡¥ï‡µç‡¥ï‡µç Josh Talks ‡¥µ‡µÄ‡¥°‡¥ø‡¥Ø‡µã‡¥ï‡¥≥‡¥ø‡µΩ ‡¥®‡¥ø‡¥ô‡µç‡¥ô‡¥≥‡µÅ‡¥ü‡µÜ ‡¥¨‡µç‡¥∞‡¥æ‡µª‡¥°‡µç ‡¥™‡µç‡¥∞‡¥¶‡µº‡¥∂‡¥ø‡¥™‡µç‡¥™‡¥ø‡¥ï‡µç‡¥ï‡¥æ‡¥®‡µÅ‡¥Ç ‡¥™‡¥∞‡¥∏‡µç‡¥Ø‡¥Ç ‡¥ö‡µÜ‡¥Ø‡µç‡¥Ø‡¥æ‡¥®‡µÅ‡¥Ç varun@joshtalks.com  ‡¥á‡µΩ Connect ‡¥ö‡µÜ‡¥Ø‡µç‡¥Ø‡µÇ.
If you find this talk helpful, please like and share it and let us know in the comments box.
You can now showcase and advertise your brand on the Josh Talks videos, reach out to us at varun@joshtalks.com if you are interested.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalees. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 9 languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the setbacks they face in their career and helping them discover their true calling in life.
